      <div class="content">
        <h2>About Big Bowl</h2>
        <p>There’s really only one place for authentic Chinese and Thai food and that’s Big Bowl. Big Bowl believes that the best food is made from scratch. Starting with with the highest quality ingredients and locally grown produce, you can taste big, bold layers of flavors in every dish. Everyone raves about the pad Thai, homemade curries, dipping sauces, spicy dishes, and our create-your-own stir-fry. Each element adds up to big taste and takes our food to another level. Be it a fresh squeeze of lime, homemade ginger ales, fragrant herbs or the seared Thai chilies, Big Bowl is big on authentic. </p>
